---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Contact Us"
  description="Get in touch with RemoteWorkHQ. Questions, suggestions, or feedback — we would love to hear from you."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900">Contact Us</h1>
        <div class="mt-10 prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none">
          <p>
            Have a question, suggestion, or feedback? Found a bug in one of our tools? We would love to hear from you.
          </p>

          <h2>Email</h2>
          <p>
            The best way to reach us: <a href="mailto:hello@remoteworkhq.com">hello@remoteworkhq.com</a>
          </p>
          <p>
            We aim to respond within 24-48 hours on business days.
          </p>

          <h2>What to Contact Us About</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Tool feedback</strong> — Found a bug or have an idea to improve one of our free tools? Let us know.</li>
            <li><strong>Content suggestions</strong> — Is there a topic you would like us to cover? Tell us what you need.</li>
            <li><strong>Corrections</strong> — If you spot an error in one of our articles, please let us know so we can fix it.</li>
            <li><strong>Partnerships</strong> — Interested in collaborating? Reach out.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Press & Media</h2>
          <p>
            For press inquiries, please email <a href="mailto:hello@remoteworkhq.com">hello@remoteworkhq.com</a> with "Press" in the subject line.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-10 rounded-2xl bg-gray-50 p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Before You Email</h3>
            <ul class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-1">
              <li>All our tools are free and run in your browser — no account needed.</li>
              <li>We do not accept guest posts or sponsored content.</li>
              <li>We do not sell backlinks.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
